value.string: This Time Interval is situated on the second floor with one bed/one bath in Tower I. Enjoy Halloween and early November on Beautiful Kaanapali Beach. The Whaler on Kaanapali Beach offers amenities that include an ocean view pool along the famed Kaanapali Beach walk, spa, sauna, workout gym, salon, underground parking, and a business hub center. Take a walk in the center courtyard while enjoying the tropical landscaping and Koi fish pond. Seller financing is available to qualified buyers with 30-50% down, 3-5 years at 5-6% interest.

Breathtaking views from this Tower II inner courtyard 11th floor studio at the Whaler. Interval R dates run from August 19 to September 2. Remodeled in 2010, this apartment has all new furniture, accessories and stainless steel appliances. Also upgraded were the kitchen and bath with new granite counter tops, hardwood cabinets and tiled floors. While enjoying a cool beverage from the lanai you will savor the views down Kaanapali Beach to Black Rock, the lush West Maui mountains, and the breaking surf of the beautiful Pacific. The Whaler offers amenities such as barbecues, a beach side pool, spa, sauna, workout gym, salon, underground parking and a business hub center. The newly renovated courtyard boasts a koi fish pond, tropical landscaping and plenty of space to enjoy this tranquil location featuring the best of Maui and Kaanapali Resort.
